	<h1 class="post-headline" data-remote="post:2184:title">
		Coronavirus is Keeping Prison Families From Saying Their Last Goodbyes
	</h1>
	<h4 class="post-deck" data-remote="post:2184:deck">
		Some relatives can’t claim bodies or hold funerals amid COVID-19 restrictions.
	</h4>
</div>


  <article class="post-2184">

    <aside class="col4">
      <div class="inner">

        <div class="post-byline">
            by <span><a href="http://www.themarshallproject.org/staff/nicole-lewis">Nicole Lewis</a></span> and <span><a href="http://www.themarshallproject.org/staff/maurice-chammah">Maurice Chammah</a></span>

        </div>
          <div class="post-byline-shim"></div>

        
